---
description: PodoKit project conventions (stack, commands, code style, tooling)
alwaysApply: true
---

The conventions for this project are documented in [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md)
at the repository root. Follow them: web runs on :5001 and api on :5002; use
shadcn-svelte components and the shared `DataTable`/`TableToolbar` for lists;
Svelte 5 runes only; branch on the error `code`, not the message; keep strings in
i18n; and respect the `.podokit/` file-ownership tiers (never hand-edit
`// podokit:` fenced regions or `src/lib/components/ui/**`).
